# Data Dictionary — sciscinet_sample.parquet (Bentley et al. 2023)
40K SciSciNet sample. Cols: paper_id, year, author_count, institution_count,
reference_count, citation_count, citation_count_5y, disruption_score, novelty_score,
conventionality_score, doc_type. Key: year, disruption_score (CD5), citation_count (weight).
